<PageTitle>B2 Hosting and Render Modes</PageTitle>

<h1>B2. Hosting Model and Render Modes</h1>

<p>
	This sample compares static SSR and interactive server rendering in a single Blazor Web App.
</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Counter</strong>: Uses <code>@@rendermode InteractiveServer</code> so button clicks are interactive.</li>
	<li><strong>Weather</strong>: Demonstrates streaming SSR with server-rendered content.</li>
	<li><strong>Prerender Probe</strong>: Shows when the component becomes interactive.</li>
</ul>
